    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DOTS Survivors is a casual action game where you play as an astronaut exploring the cosmos fending off hostile aliens along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your ideal character build from two dozen unique weapons and powerups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326810/extras/aa684ba23fd31cf2e7bc30e361bb669c.avif?t=1756840675\" width=788 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons to choose:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oxygen Hose Whip</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Jetpack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Radioactive Waste Drops</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drone Swarm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mega Laser Strike</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Screwdriver Shot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sawblade Scatter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satellite Dish Toss</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CO2 Vent</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plasma Blaster</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Black Hole</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >O.M.G. Wrench</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade your capabilities to defeat more aliens!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326810/extras/ccfd0ee3d26925b776811f7d78e55983.avif?t=1756840675\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326810/extras_big/ccfd0ee3d26925b776811f7d78e55983.avif?t=1756840675 width=800 height=442 /></span><strong>Fight off waves of alien foes!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326810/extras/d4bf4e615af47cda8325521558dc672f.avif?t=1756840675\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326810/extras_big/d4bf4e615af47cda8325521558dc672f.avif?t=1756840675 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong>Discover more hostile aliens!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326810/extras/fbb75dd53ae48818e077db869fd2a4c3.avif?t=1756840675\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326810/extras_big/fbb75dd53ae48818e077db869fd2a4c3.avif?t=1756840675 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This project serves as an example of the performance and game architecture made possible by Unity's Data-Oriented Technology Stack (DOTS).</p>",
